    "evening": "打羽毛球。",
    "morning": "本科《中国古代文学史（唐宋卷）》授课，多了很多学生，原来是被吉他吸引来的。",
    "night": "",
    "noon": "午餐，和同事聊课程思政案例，借鉴了别人的写作思路。"
  },
  "comments": [
    {
      "author": "123",
      "text": "今天和他讨论了他喜欢的电视剧，我发表了和他相反的看法，他生气不理我了，我已经示弱了，可是他还是生气不理我，我觉得先让彼此都冷静一下吧，明天再去找他，而且我因为他因为一部电视剧不理我了，也有点小失落。明天再和好吧，并且我知道以后不能跟他讨论他喜欢的电视剧偶像时发表恶评，这是他很在乎的东西。我不能明知他在乎还评价",
      "timestamp": "2026/3/12 00:45:56"
    }
  ],
  "completed": false,
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "早啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "今早阳光很好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:22",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "雪落在地上被阳光照耀",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "很美的一个早晨，但我又做了黑暗料理",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "《麦芽糖炒糖醋排骨》",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "做糊了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "笑不出来了...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "麦芽糖是什么鬼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "正常不都是白醋吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "我做的是特别版本的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "这次不是我灵机一动",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "我小时候吃过一个苍南美食，就是麦芽糖拌的排骨",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "很好吃",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "不是那种白糖的傻甜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "糖的甜度还有分傻不傻的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "还有聪明的糖吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "麦芽糖的甜就是很，就是很灵的甜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "我为麦芽糖发声!!!",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "你怎么喜欢吃这种甜不拉几的东西啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "我还喜欢喝奶茶...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "你会觉得我奇怪吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "不会啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "吃好吃的甜食很幸福",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "吃齁甜的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "不开心",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh还蛮可爱的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你喜欢草莓味的东西吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "喜欢啊，我喜欢吃草莓味的泡泡糖和阿尔卑斯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "我去，怎么不早说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "真的有点可爱了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "你们苏州没有那种奇奇怪怪的小甜食吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "梅花糕算不算？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "梅花糕是很正派的好吃",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "传统 经典",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯我觉得苏州应该有吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "你们那边也有好甜口的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯嗯嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊，我这里的东坡肉做的很甜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "东坡肉不喜欢，太肥腻了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "我喜欢奇奇怪怪的小甜食，还得是中式的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "我小时候吃过栀子花炒蛋",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "超级香！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:36"
    },
    {
      "content": " 啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "这又是什么黑暗料理？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "你的记忆没出错吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "不黑暗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "栀子花很香，蛋很嫩，炒菜中和了枝子花过于浓郁的香气",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "吃起来就刚刚好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "栀子花说：\"去你妈的，我就是要这样香，香得痛痛快快，你们他妈的管得着吗！\"",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "？？？no",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "栀子花怎么突然骂人？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "你在借栀子花骂我吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh不是啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "是汪曾祺的一个名句，描写栀子花的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "我的家乡人说是：\"碰鼻子香\"。栀子花粗粗大大，又香得掸都掸不开，于是为文雅人不取，以为品格不高。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "栀子花说：\"去你妈的，我就是要这样香，香得痛痛快快，你们他妈的管得着吗！\"",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "汪曾祺我知道",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "小学语文课写过他的家乡鸭蛋还是什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊，高邮鸭蛋，蛋黄流油，金黄灿烂",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "对对对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "在我还当文青的时候，栀子花很出名",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "？？？栀子花？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是不是想说汪曾祺？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh没错",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉他是个很有趣的小老头",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊，他非常的有趣，好玩",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "在文革受苦那批作家里面属他心态最好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "你有空的话可以看看他想问人间草木",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "好啊（虽然可能永远没空去看了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "没事，把它先放在自己的脑子里",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "说不定哪天就想起来去看了，这就是最好的缘分",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，我还是要跟你极力安利一下栀子花炒蛋",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "如果汪曾祺吃过这个菜，那这个菜也会出现在我们小学课本里",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "没吃过诶",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "花瓣做菜不会奇怪吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "不会奇怪，我只是做菜黑暗，但我的口味并不黑暗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "这应该是浙江的特色菜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "是小时候我妈去苍南玩，给我带回来的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "你想试驾的话，得去浙菜馆找找",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉你妈很爱你啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "爱啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "算了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "愉快的周末中午",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "似乎并不是讨论原生家庭的好时机。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "闭麦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "你起床了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "你那里今天有太阳吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "阴天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "那就再躺一会吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "你今天有什么安排没有？?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "昨天安排过了，今天懒得动",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "你不会还没吃上午饭吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "周末这个点不吃午饭不是很正常？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "快点点外卖吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "我想不到吃什么，好烦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "“栀子花炒蛋”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh不吃",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，我刚搜了下，你们江苏的特色小甜食是油桂花糖年糕",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "要不要中午吃这个？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "我操，你还去搜了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "你说没有",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得江苏这么人杰地灵的地方不可能没有特色中式甜食",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "你吃过桂花糖炒年糕吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "吃过啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "我没吃过，你替我吃一下吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1772933111418317200.jpg]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "可我吃了你又吃不到",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "没关系",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "我会想象，你只要跟我说好不好吃就行",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "行吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "reasoning_chain": "我预感到接下来说的话可能会惹他生气，但我又不想和他真的以后不聊天，所以我要事先示弱说明",
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我中午就点这个",
